WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.356
Ejection fraction trajectory diverges sharply by histology.

00:00:03.356 --> 00:00:06.712
Lymphocytic myocarditis typically recovers over six to

00:00:06.712 --> 00:00:07.671
twelve months.

00:00:07.671 --> 00:00:11.026
Giant cell myocarditis follows a progressive decline.

00:00:11.026 --> 00:00:14.382
Twenty-one percent of cases progress to dilated

00:00:14.382 --> 00:00:16.300
cardiomyopathy within five years.
